OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FWords by Deputy Content Editor Eloise
OL,7,FLinford
OL,9,FAs conflict in the Middle East impacts
OL,10,Fenergy prices in the UK, the question
OL,11,Faround whether Britain should be
OL,12,Fdrilling in the North Sea has become
OL,13,Fone of the most divisive political
OL,14,Ftopics in recent weeks.
OL,16,FThe fate of Jackdaw, a new major gas
OL,17,Ffield off the coast of Aberdeen, hangs
OL,18,Fin the balance with its operators
OL,19,Fclaiming it could produce enough
OL,20,Fenergy to heat more than 1.4 million
OL,21,Fhomes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
