PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775732571
OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FHowever, the move would push the
OL,7,Fgovernment even further from its net-
OL,8,Fzero targets, which played a major
OL,9,Fpart in its manifesto pledge.
OL,11,FSome UK politicians say they plan to
OL,12,Fimmediately stop all fossil fuel
OL,13,Fproduction, while others vow to "drill
OL,14,Fbaby, drill".
OL,16,FITV News sets out the stances of the
OL,17,Fmain political parties.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
