OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775732571
OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FThe government continues to press
OL,7,Fforward with its manifesto promise of
OL,8,Fclean power by 2030 by focusing on
OL,9,Frenewable energy and nuclear power.
OL,11,FIt pledged to maintain "a strategic
OL,12,Freserve of gas power stations to
OL,13,Fguarantee security of supply" but
OL,14,Ftransition away from fossil fuels in a
OL,15,F"phased and responsible" way.
OL,17,FEnergy Secretary Ed Miliband, one of
OL,18,Fthe most vocal opponents of new
OL,19,Fdrilling, has faced backlash in recent
OL,20,Fweeks over his staunch position.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
