OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775732571
OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FHe has denied claims new licenses
OL,7,Fwould bring large financial gain,
OL,8,Ftelling ITV News last week: "Those
OL,9,Fpeople who say new exploration
OL,10,Flicenses will somehow create huge
OL,11,Famounts of energy for us... I mean,
OL,12,Fthey're just wrong."
OL,14,FEarlier this month, the Times reported
OL,15,Fthat Miliband was set to approve
OL,16,FJackdaw but the government says that
OL,17,Fspeculation is "incorrect".
OL,19,FIt is understood the Jackdaw field has
OL,20,Fbeen subject to internal Labour debate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
