OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FHowever, Scottish Labour Leader Anas
OL,7,FSarwar has broken ranks with his own
OL,8,Fparty to suggest more oil and gas
OL,9,Fdrilling should be approved.
OL,11,FHe said last week that a "balanced
OL,12,Fapproach" is needed on the issue of
OL,13,Fenergy.
