OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FSarwar added: It means supporting oil
OL,7,Fand gas, which has a role to play for
OL,8,Fdecades to come, it means investing in
OL,9,Fthe huge renewables potential of our
OL,10,Fgreat country, but it also means
OL,11,Fending the ideological block to clean
OL,12,Fnuclear energy that currently exists
OL,13,Fin Scotland to unlock billions of
OL,14,Fpounds of investment, thousands of new
OL,15,Fjobs and greater energy security."
OL,17,FConservatives
OL,26,@wD@bO]
