OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FThe Tories are in favour of drilling
OL,7,Fand last month pledged to reduce legal
OL,8,Fobstacles which prevent new oil and
OL,9,Fgas projects being approved.
OL,11,FLaunching her party's Get Britain
OL,12,FDrilling Now Bill, Conservative Leader
OL,13,FKemi Badenoch said drilling is "the
OL,14,Fonly way we can protect families from
OL,15,Frising bills, keep the cost of energy
OL,16,Fdown for business, and control
OL,17,Finflation".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
