PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775732571
OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FThe bill proposes to remove the
OL,7,Frequirement for downstream emissions
OL,8,Fto be considered in planning
OL,9,Fdecisions, therefore reversing the
OL,10,Fruling to block the development of the
OL,11,FRosebank site in the North Sea.
OL,13,FThe party claims more drilling would
OL,14,Fsecure cheap, reliable energy and cut
OL,15,Fenergy bills - in addition to making
OL,16,FBritain more resilient to global
OL,17,Fenergy supply and price shock.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/27
