OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FBadenoch said: "We need to get Britain
OL,7,Fdrilling in the North Sea. It's good
OL,8,Ffor our energy security, our financial
OL,9,Fsecurity, and our national security.
OL,11,F"Keir Starmer hides behind legal
OL,12,Fprocess because he doesn't have the
OL,13,Fbackbone to stand up to Ed Miliband.
OL,15,F"The Conservatives have had enough.
OL,16,FThis Bill would stop the lawfare and
OL,17,Ffree our oil and gas industry to start
OL,18,Fdrilling, creating new jobs and
OL,19,Fbringing in revenue to get energy
OL,20,Fbills down.
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@AOU
