OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,F"This is another step in our cheap
OL,7,Fpower plan, which will cut bills by
OL,8,F#200 and ensure a stronger economy and
OL,9,Fa stronger country."
OL,11,FLiberal Democrats
OL,13,FMeanwhile, the Liberal Democrats
OL,14,Finsist there should be a managed
OL,15,Ftransition away from fossil fuels.
OL,17,FLeader Sir Ed Davey, who served as
OL,18,FEnergy Secretary from 2012 to 2015,
OL,19,Fcalled Badenoch's figures "nonsense".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@TO]
