OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FSpeaking to journalists last week, he
OL,7,Fsaid: "She says that we can get #2.5
OL,8,Fbillion extra in tax revenue and that
OL,9,Fwill help cut bills. She's just lying.
OL,11,F"They would not have enough any extra
OL,12,Fmoney to help people in the in the
OL,13,Ffirst few years of her policy. So I
OL,14,Fthink that's quite outrageous that
OL,15,Fshe's misleading British people."
OL,17,FHowever, he did concede that "we're
OL,18,Fgoing to need lots of oil and gas in
OL,19,Fthe years to come" and that the
OL,20,FJackdaw gas field could be part of
OL,21,Fthat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/27
