OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FGreen Party
OL,8,FPerhaps unsurprisingly, the Green
OL,9,FParty has the hardest anti-drilling
OL,10,Fstance of all parties.
OL,12,F"The Green Party is clear: stop new
OL,13,Foil and gas, close the loopholes, and
OL,14,Finvest properly in the transition to
OL,15,Frenewable energy," said Green MP
OL,16,FHannah Spencer at the end of March.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
