OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FShe also refuted Badenoch's claims
OL,7,Fthat new drilling will result in
OL,8,Fcheaper energy bills, saying:
OL,9,F"Hundreds of licences issued between
OL,10,F2010 and 2024 have delivered the
OL,11,Fequivalent of just 36 days' extra gas.
OL,13,F"Labour's position isn't good enough
OL,14,Feither. A 'ban' on new licences
OL,15,Fdoesn't mean much if loopholes like
OL,16,Ftiebacks still allow new drilling to
OL,17,Fgo ahead."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
