OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FIn a post on X on Friday, Green Party
OL,7,Fleader Zack Polanski accused Miliband
OL,8,Fof selling the country out, amid
OL,9,Freports he was set to approve plans
OL,10,Ffor Jackdaw.
OL,12,FHe wrote: "Ed Miliband has sold us all
OL,13,Fout.
OL,15,F"The climate movement, the
OL,16,Fenvironmental sector - and most
OL,17,Fimportantly - our future generations.
OL,19,F"No longer can Labour claim to have
OL,20,Fthe odd minister who "gets it."
OL,21,FThey're bought and paid for."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
