OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FReform UK is staunchly pro-drilling
OL,7,Fand go as far as wanting to scrap what
OL,8,FRobert Jenrick calls "a lot of the net
OL,9,Fzero madness", which he claims would
OL,10,Fsave the country #13 billion a year.
OL,12,FThe party would scrap the scheme
OL,13,Fproviding grants to homeowners to
OL,14,Finstall heat pumps, cut investment in
OL,15,Fcarbon capture technologies, and axe
OL,16,Fgrants for new electric vehicles, the
OL,17,Fparty's Treasury spokesperson said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
