OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FParty leader Nigel Farage - who has
OL,7,Frepeated Donald Trump's slogan of
OL,8,F"drill baby, drill" - believes opening
OL,9,Fup licences to drill will lead to
OL,10,F"thousands of jobs, increased tax
OL,11,Frevenues and cheaper gas prices".
