OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FSpeaking on Tuesday, Farage said: "The
OL,7,FUK is the most vulnerable to an energy
OL,8,Fprice shock of any country because we
OL,9,Frefuse. We refuse to produce the oil
OL,10,Fand gas in our country, both offshore
OL,11,Fand onshore, that we should be
OL,12,Fproducing."
OL,14,FDuncan Massey, a Reform UK councillor
OL,15,Fin Aberdeen, around 250km from the
OL,16,FJackdaw site, previously said: "The
OL,17,FNorth Sea oil and gas industry has a
OL,18,Fgreat and vital future if we get our
OL,19,Fpolicies right."
OL,26,@xD@`OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/27
