OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775732571
OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FHe continued: "Renewables can be part
OL,7,Fof the UK energy mix. But the sky-high
OL,8,Fsubsidies that they need to go ahead
OL,9,Fare simply not justifiable or
OL,10,Fsustainable."
OL,12,FScottish National Party
OL,14,FScotland's First Minister has softened
OL,15,Fhis government's position on domestic
OL,16,Foil and gas drilling as the crisis in
OL,17,Fthe Middle East began to take effect
OL,18,Fon energy prices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/27
