OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FSNP-led governments in recent years
OL,7,Fhave been cautious about further
OL,8,Fdrilling in the North Sea, despite
OL,9,Fpressure from the industry and
OL,10,Fopposition parties.
OL,12,FHowever, speaking at a live recording
OL,13,Fof the Holyrood Sources podcast on
OL,14,FThursday, John Swinney appeared to
OL,15,Fchange his stance following the
OL,16,Fblocking of the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
