OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775732571
OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FHe said: "I can't give you a
OL,7,Fdefinitive answer on Jackdaw and
OL,8,FRosebank, because the climate
OL,9,Fcompatibility assessment has got to be
OL,10,Fundertaken...
OL,12,F"What I'm saying to you is I think
OL,13,Fwe've got to look at the geo-political
OL,14,Fsituation that we now face and
OL,15,Frecognise that we are experiencing
OL,16,Fmuch greater risk to our energy
OL,17,Fsecurity as a consequence of what's
OL,18,Fhappening there."
