OL,6,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,7,Four political experts are across all
OL,8,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,9,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,11,FWhat is the Jackdaw gas field?
OL,13,FJackdaw is a proposed new gas field
OL,14,Faround 250km off the coast of
OL,15,FAberdeen, led by Shell-affiliate BG
OL,16,FInternational.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/27
