OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FThose behind the project say that at
OL,7,Fpeak production Jackdaw is expected to
OL,8,Fcontribute around 6.5% of UK
OL,9,FContinental Shelf gas production,
OL,10,Fwhich would make enough energy to heat
OL,11,Fmore than 1.4 million homes.
OL,13,FPlans were approved in 2022 but the
OL,14,Fproject was halted by the Supreme
OL,15,FCourt in 2024, after a ruling that
OL,16,Femissions created by burning fossil
OL,17,Ffuels should be considered when
OL,18,Fgranting planning permission for new
OL,19,Fdrilling sites.
OL,21,FWhat about other organisations?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
