OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FLord John Browne, former chief
OL,7,Fexecutive of BP, said the Jackdaw
OL,8,Ffield should "absolutely" be approved.
OL,10,FHe told BBC Radio 4's Today programme:
OL,11,F"We need all forms of energy, and we
OL,12,Fneed to make sure that we have a
OL,13,Fdiversified source. We don't have
OL,14,Fenough diversification today to take
OL,15,Fcare of crises in the future.
OL,17,F"The question of the North Sea, there
OL,18,Fare a couple of fields which are
OL,19,Fpartly developed. They should be fully
OL,20,Fdeveloped and go ahead."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
