OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FDavid Whitehouse, chief executive of
OL,7,FOffshore Energies UK, said: "This is
OL,8,Fnot an either renewables or oil and
OL,9,Fgas scenario.
OL,11,F"We urgently need greater supplies of
OL,12,Fsecure, domestically produced energy
OL,13,Fincluding oil and gas, which will
OL,14,Fremain a critical part of the UK
OL,15,Fenergy system and economy for decades."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G24/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
