OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,FPhilip Evans, senior climate
OL,7,Fcampaigner at Greenpeace UK, said:
OL,8,F"Jackdaw, and any new drilling in the
OL,9,FNorth Sea, will produce millions of
OL,10,Ftonnes of CO2 and vast methane leaks,
OL,11,Faccelerating climate change and
OL,12,Fincreasing the costs we all pay for
OL,13,Fextreme weather.
OL,15,F"This is the hard truth that fossil
OL,16,Ffuel promoters want us to ignore ` our
OL,17,Ffossil fuels are provided by a
OL,18,Fvolatile global market which we cannot
OL,19,Fcontrol and is regularly upturned by
OL,20,Freckless wars and blockades.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G25/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
