CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775732571
OL,3,CWhat does each political party think
OL,4,Cabout North Sea drilling?
OL,6,F"The little that is left in the North
OL,7,FSea is completely inadequate to
OL,8,Fprovide an escape route from that doom
OL,9,Floop, something those calling for more
OL,10,Fdrilling have no intention of
OL,11,Fattempting.
OL,13,F"The only path to real security is to
OL,14,Fleave fossil fuels behind as quickly
OL,15,Fas possible."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G26/27
